last_episode_to_air.overview: Ji Woon's surgery commences, and the Haneul Group vote on their future. Seo Woo makes a decision about his career.

name: Cinderella and Four Knights
overview: Eun Ha-Won is a college student. She is a bright girl who wants to be a veterinarian, but at home she is lonely. She is isolated from her family members. Eun Ha-Won lives with father, step-mother and step-sister after her mother died in a car accident. One day, she helps a mysterious old man. The old man suggests to her to live in a mansion and pursue her dream of becoming a veterinarian. Since than, she moves into the mansion and lives with three cousins Kang Ji-Woon, Kang Hyun-Min, Kang Seo-Woo and their bodyguard Lee Yoon-Sung.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Eun Ha Won is a young woman with 10 part-time jobs, trying to earn money to go to college. When she realizes an accounting mistake will sap her of her savings, she agrees to haughty rich boy Kang Hyun Min's ironic request to join him at his chairman grandfather's fifth wedding.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Chairman Kang, in light of Ha Won's behavior at his wedding, offers her a tantalizing deal that could solve all of her problems.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Ha Won agrees to move into Sky House, but is trepid about what will meet her there. Hyun Min decides to carry on his joke of being engaged to Ha Won.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Hyun Min realizes that Ha Won isn't enamored with his money and finds her irresistible because of it. Chairman Kang gives Ha Won her first assignment, get the three Kang Cousins to eat a meal together.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Chairman Kang honors his three dead sons on the same day every year, and Ha Won is tasked with making sure the grandsons attend.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: On the day of her graduation, Ha Won realizes that she didn't fulfill her side of the bargain, and leaves Sky House. Having nowhere to go, an unexpected ally appears.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Ha Won's new assignment is to get the boys to go on a trip together. Realizing it is possibly her most difficult task yet, she enlists the aid of some allies to aid in her cause.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: The forced retreat is here, and the Kang Cousins come willingly. Well, most of them. Ha Won wants a wholesome time with friends, but Hye Ji has an ulterior motive.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: After a night of drunken revery, the Kang Cousins have some regrets. Ha Won injures both her pride and her ankle.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Ha Won uses her injury to her advantage. A potent "love square" emerges. Secretary Lee is put in an awkward situation.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Ha Won is confused by the dynamic of a new house-guest at Sky House. Hyun Min tries desperately to be a good person, but isn't sure he knows how.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Yoo Na pivots to a new target when she realizes Hyun Min isn't paying attention to her. A figure from Ha Won's past emerges, and his goals appear to be less than sincere.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Ji Woon confesses his feelings, which brings up a world of potential trouble at Sky House. Hyun Min confesses feelings of his own. Chairman Kang appears not to have any feelings.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: When Chairman Kang collapses, the boys all get tested to see if they can match as potential donors.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: Ji Woon intends to get what could be his last chance at a date with Ha Won. Hyun Min takes a stand against those trying to take over Haneul Group.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Ji Woon's surgery commences, and the Haneul Group vote on their future. Seo Woo makes a decision about his career.
